PERFECT TROPICAL OASIS WITH CIRCULAR DRIVEWAY, HUGE BONUS ROOM THAT CAN EASILY BE USED AS A 3RD BEDR! AC 2018 WITH NEW DUCTS IN 2022. TANKLESS WATER HEATER 2019, WHIRPOOL WASHER, DRYER 2020. LARGE UPGRADED KITCHEN BOASTS HIGH END STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS & WOOD CABINETRY. INCLUDED IN YOUR WONDERLAND ARE COCONUT PALM AND BANANA TREES WITH VEGETABLE GARDENS THAT YEILD BROCOLI, CABBAGE & TOMATOES.
